&lt;h3&gt;Behaviours&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p id=&quot;B1&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;B1&lt;/strong&gt;: Prioritises health, safety and environment when undertaking work&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id=&quot;B2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;B2&lt;/strong&gt;: Adaptable, for example willing to accept changing priorities and working requirements&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id=&quot;B3&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;B3&lt;/strong&gt;: Team player, for example keeps others informed, recognises personal and professional limitations and seeks advice when necessary&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id=&quot;B4&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;B4&lt;/strong&gt;: Professional, for example punctual, trustworthy, polite, courteous, presentable, maintains security of business specific and personal data, takes account of equality and diversity in interactions&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id=&quot;B5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;B5&lt;/strong&gt;: Self-motivated, for example manages own time effectively, takes responsibility to complete the job&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id=&quot;B6&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;B6&lt;/strong&gt;: Pride in work, for example works to agreed quality targets and standards&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id=&quot;B7&quot; data-ksb-filter=&quot;29f33d3e-c7ff-4d61-a73a-9a4d43f8c5b5,29f33d3e-c7ff-4d61-a73a-9a4d43f8c5b5,29f33d3e-c7ff-4d61-a73a-9a4d43f8c5b5,29f33d3e-c7ff-4d61-a73a-9a4d43f8c5b5,b3d3ca9e-784b-4013-b376-0a946344f2df,b3d3ca9e-784b-4013-b376-0a946344f2df,b3d3ca9e-784b-4013-b376-0a946344f2df,b3d3ca9e-784b-4013-b376-0a946344f2df&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;B7&lt;/strong&gt;: Committed to continued professional development&lt;/p&gt;
